{"article_id":"t2bwrJhjGTnsyyBO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"( CNN )","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Reporters and editors at the Capital Gazette quickly turned their heads around","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"when the glass doors","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"leading to the newsroom","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"suddenly shattered .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Within minutes , it `` was like a war zone . ''","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"`` He was going down our newsroom ,","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"starting from the front","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"and just continually shooting people , ''","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Phil Davis , a police reporter at the newspaper said .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"The shooting","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"that marked the deadliest day for US journalism since 9/11","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"began","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"when a gunman made his way through a brown four-story office building just a few miles outside downtown Annapolis","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"-- the historic Maryland capital city .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"Armed with a shotgun ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"the gunman opened fire through the front doors of the newsroom around 3 p.m .","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"Four employees were killed at the scene ;","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"a fifth person ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"who was shot in the upper body and arm ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"died at the hospital .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"Keith Cyphers was on the phone with a client at his office across the hallway from the newspaper","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"when he heard a loud noise","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"and saw the gunman .","depth":6},{"id":24,"text":"`` The door of the Capital Gazette had been blown to pieces .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"It was in shattered pieces all on the carpet","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"and this guy was holding what looked like a big shotgun","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"and moving across the entrance of the Capital Gazette office","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"pointing the gun deeper into the office","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"like he was targeting people , ''","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"he told CNN affiliate WJLA","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"When the gunman walked inside ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"he could easily see the entire newsroom .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Most of the staff were at their desks","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"and the editors were in their offices","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"lined up on the left .","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` It 's a completely open newsroom , ''","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"said Terry Smith , a columnist for the Capital Gazette .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"`` There are glass windows all around the room .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"There is nothing except for a few half-walls at the editors ' offices on the left","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"to impede a shooter , ''","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"he added .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Another reporter , Selene San Felice , said","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"she heard the first shots","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"and grabbed her purse","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"before heading to a nearby back door .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Two other staffers and an intern","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"who were also trying to get away","depth":11},{"id":48,"text":"joined her ,","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"but the door was locked .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"With nowhere","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"to go ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"she hid under a desk with an intern .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Another woman got behind a filing cabinet","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"after falling to the floor .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"John McNamara , one of the five employees","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"who died ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"kept trying to open the door .","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"But the gunman had barricaded the back entrance of the paper 's office","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"so people could not escape","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"as he began `` systematically hunting","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"and killing , ''","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"state 's attorney Wes Adams said at a hearing Friday .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"The shooter `` was there","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"to kill as many people","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"as he could get , ''","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Anne Arundel County police Chief Timothy Altomare said at a news conference .","depth":6},{"id":67,"text":"`` I 'm not sure exactly in the next couple seconds what happened ,","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"but I know","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"that John was standing up , ''","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"San Felice said .","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"`` I heard the footsteps ,","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"and John got shot .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"It was very close .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"I saw him get shot ,","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"but I did n't see the gunman or anything . ''","depth":8},{"id":76,"text":"There were no screams .","depth":8},{"id":77,"text":"It was all silence and the sound of gunshots","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"traveling through the newsroom of one of the oldest newspapers in the country ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"reporters recalled .","depth":7},{"id":80,"text":"San Felice could hear the gunman 's footsteps","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"as she sat under a desk .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"She was praying","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"and texted her parents","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"to tell them","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"that she loved them .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"Trying to go unnoticed ,","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"she also attempted to call 911 .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"`` I 'm sure","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"I was breathing really loud ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"and I was trying not to ,","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"but I just --","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"I could n't be quiet , ''","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"she said .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Next to her , summer intern Anthony Messenger took his phone","depth":7},{"id":95,"text":"and tweeted ,","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"`` Active shooter 888 Bestgate please help us . ''","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"Davis","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"who was also hiding under a desk","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"he wondered to himself ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"`` Are we all going to die ? ''","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"when he heard the gunman reload .","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"`` I 'm a police reporter .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"I write about this stuff","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"-- not necessarily to this extent , but shootings and death -- all the time , ''","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"he told the Baltimore Sun .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"`` But as much as I 'm going to try to articulate how traumatizing it is to be hiding under your desk ,","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"you do n't know","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"until you 're there","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"and you feel helpless . ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":221,"left":0,"right":220,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":220,"left":130,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":119,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":114,"right":118,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":1,"right":113,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":112,"right":4,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":112,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":5,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":116,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":6,"right":115,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":7,"right":8,"